    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《梅卡妮可 -兔子与水星之谣-》是由日本知名独立游戏社团Loser/s制作，OTAKU Plan汉化发行的一款赛博朋克、时间轮回系解谜RPG游戏。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>声明：本游戏内登场角色均已超过18岁。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>★★★操作提示：按下F5即可返回游戏主界面，读取存档★★★</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■赛博朋克</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1558510/extras/044c700cf8e1e87b18d22bedb37c66cf.avif?t=1770344755\" width=624 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事背景是公元5029年，位于水星上的日本领土，充斥着霓虹灯牌与醉鬼的城市『断头台』。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遮蔽着太阳的『天盖』之下，是星光不可及的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■时间轮回</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1558510/extras/a50cfdc091ef307d288e12b7cf4d73a7.avif?t=1770344755\" width=624 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每三天就要毁灭一次的绝望情形之下，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角和有着兔耳朵的机械女仆不言放弃地在绝望中挣扎，寻找事件的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■RPG×音楽</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1558510/extras/c4a64de08a4dd045967ca87da0f3b321.avif?t=1770344755\" width=624 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作虽然是RPG，但是摈弃了战斗内容，你需要通过演奏音乐，从城里的居民口中获得贵重的情报，去解锁下一步的剧情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■解谜</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1558510/extras/f6058ec83cd113dea9f2f369399ae6fd.avif?t=1770344755\" width=624 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将在美轮美奂的赛博朋克风2D世界里探索，向水星的居民们演奏音乐来收集情报，最终达到拯救世界的目的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■魅力十足的角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1558510/extras/6e10e476780ba469baa539fdc3f04777.avif?t=1770344755\" width=624 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >居民中不乏来自其他宇宙的语言学者，被剥夺了记忆与感情的大罪人，情感洋溢的虚拟艺术家……。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽情体验与未来人的奇妙邂逅吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赛博朋克背景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时间轮回系剧情</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的解谜要素</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别具一格的音乐演奏</p></li></ul>",
